Date: Mon, 2 Mar 2026 11:08:06 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add complete backend - API routes, RunPod REST API,
 ComfyUI client, workflow engine

- app/api/pods: Create/manage RunPod GPU pods via REST API
- app/api/workflows/[slug]/run: Core product endpoint - run any template
- app/api/workflows/import: Analyze workflows, resolve nodes, auto-search Civitai
- app/api/models: Import from Civitai, download to pod
- app/api/jobs: Job CRUD with plan/execute/retry/cancel
- app/api/debug: Diagnostic endpoint for env var checking
- lib/runpod.ts: RunPod REST + GraphQL client
- lib/comfyui.ts: ComfyUI remote API client with patchWorkflow
- lib/node-registry.ts: 20+ node packs, 400+ class_types mapped
- lib/workflow-analyzer.ts: Extract models, nodes, params from workflows
- lib/hooks.ts: React hooks for all data + useWorkflowRun
- lib/bootstrap.ts: Pod health polling and model download
- lib/db-types.ts: Full type system with status configs
